---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section class="relative h-screen w-full overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full z-0">
    <video 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60" 
      autoplay 
      muted 
      loop 
      playsinline
    >
      <source src="https://videos.pexels.com/video-files/3129671/3129671-hd_1920_1080_30fps.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-deep-bg/70 z-10"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-20 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16">
    <p class="font-sans text-accent tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-4 animate-fade-in-up">
      Análisis . Economía . Filosofía
    </p>
    
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white font-bold leading-tight mb-6 animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
      Repensando el <br/>
      <span class="italic font-light">futuro económico</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
      Un espacio de reflexión crítica donde la teoría económica se encuentra con los fundamentos filosóficos de nuestra sociedad.
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-fade-in-up delay-300">
      <a href="#about" class="px-8 py-3 bg-action hover:bg-accent text-white font-sans font-semibold rounded-sm transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        Conocer el Proyecto
      </a>
      <a href="#blog" class="px-8 py-3 border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/10 text-white font-sans rounded-sm transition-all duration-300">
        Leer Artículos
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  /* Animación simple de entrada */
  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }
  
  .delay-100 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .delay-200 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .delay-300 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>